							<h3>Becoming a Cook</h3>
							<h4></h4>
							<p>
								Becoming a cook on CookedNearby.Com is easy. Simply sign up as a cook. Be aware that there are two user types: user and cook. Only through a cook account can you offer meals.
								During the sign up process you will need to confirm that you will adhere to any and all applicable California Health
								and Safety Codes. Also keep in mind that you will not be able to order any meals on CookedNearby.Com with a cook account. You would need to sign up as a user.
							</p>
